==English==
===Etymology===
Alpenglow is a partial translation of German Alpenglühen, from Alpen, "Alps" + glühen, "to glow."

===Pronunciation===


===Noun===
'''alpenglow'''

# A rosy or reddish glow seen near sunset or sunrise on the summits of mountains, especially snow covered mountains.

